summary: Seattle-based fashion retailer Nordstrom, Inc. announced plans to open a new Nordstrom Rack in Elmwood, LA in spring 2026.

headline: VT-Cosmetics Launches K-beauty Innovation 'REEDLE SHOT' at Ulta Beauty
summary: VT-Cosmetics, the viral K-beauty brand behind "Microneedling in a Bottle," is making its official U.S. in-store debut at over 1,410 Ulta Beauty locations nationwide, starting July 13. This milestone marks the brand's first large-scale retail rollout in North America.
